{"type": "article", "id": 55377, "title": "这款防水防尘的无线耳机，淋浴游泳都能用｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-18T22:49:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51951, "name": "xFyro Audio"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 43582, "name": "ferm LIVING"}, {"id": 31486, "name": "Dreamfarm"}, {"id": 51952, "name": "Rudolph Schelling Webermann"}, {"id": 24005, "name": "Andreas Engesvik"}, {"id": 21703, "name": "Frederik Roijé"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 211, "image": "img/article/article_show/201807182159346jAXQWiOUmkP5Kac.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>ARIA Waterproof Earbuds by xFyro Audio</h3><p>眼下无线耳机市场的竞争很激烈，似乎每个厂商都能拿出来核心卖点，有的声称与所有平台兼容，有的强调电池寿命，有的可作为健身追踪器等等。</p><p>纽约工作室 xFyro Audio 的这款新品 ARIA，声称是“全球唯一一款具有 IPx67 防水等级的真正无线耳机”。IPx67 等级，意味着允许用户在健身房、淋浴房，甚至游泳池中使用。</p><p>除了防水防尘外， ARIA 的续航时间长达 32 小时，收纳盒还可为用户提供额外 24 小时的充电时间。此外，ARIA 还配备了蓝牙 5.0，只需将耳机放在智能手机附近即可实现即时配对。电容式触控表面，可让用户控制音乐播放以及激活手机上的语音助手。目前，它在众筹平台 Indiegogo 上的早鸟价格为 109 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/aria-waterproof-earbuds-bluetooth-5-32h-battery-iphone-headphones?utm_source=www.yankodesign.com&amp;utm_medium=kickbooster&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_campaign=efced3#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220039lgvNeUz4h9CyoKbj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220038bOD4Zny1tGhYSKa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220039nPeJiYN1qQ32ObFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220039SvqhDMlABZG4H9yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220039HkvNjV6lO7R9forc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220039jGzUc96MsgTODw4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220039s0dYhxne75qa3VKc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/07/18/the-aria-are-airpods-you-can-use-in-the-shower/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Rainbow by Rudolph Schelling Webermann for Normann Copenhagen</h3><p>Rainbow 是丹麦家居品牌 Normann Copenhagen 推出的一款餐垫，看名字就知道灵感来自于彩虹。德国设计师 Rudolph Schelling Webermann 充满想象力地将产品的功能性和精巧的设计，融于这个异常简单的结构之中，磁性链接，收纳方便。尼龙材料，可耐高温 200-400 度。售价 20 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/en/Products/Accessories/Kitchen-Utensils/Rainbow-Trivet-Blue-245031\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220141CWlXxLtqPymYV914.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220141sfCji3eu8KOBwXzE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220142OtCzQWsruF2dligA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220142UqGrB3v4wHQoblJz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220142rqd37nZACQ9boLHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/en/Products/Accessories/Kitchen-Utensils/Rainbow-Trivet-Green-245032\" rel=\"nofollow\">Normann Copenhagen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cloud Lamp by ferm LIVING</h3><p>同样是来自丹麦的家居品牌 ferm LIVING，这两年单开了一条儿童线，延续了其一以贯之的风格，风格极简，颜色不算鲜艳，但物件的形状都具有流利的线条感，产品本身的形状往往是图形化的，更具诗意。</p><p>比如这款云朵装饰灯，试图为儿童的房间带去轻盈和舒适。在云朵灯下，孩子们可以阅读自己喜欢的书，与自己喜欢的泰迪熊一起睡觉，或是与好友一同玩耍。提供烟熏橡木、雾粉色以及薄荷绿三种选择，售价 72 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/kids-room/kids-lamps/cloud-lamp-mint.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220224vuYQ6d5S7OWcgV9o.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220224vEIqklzUXu2wOLdf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807182202247OqVv1GTHZIRrk0y.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220225DEoc8Qa2qAMbt0g4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220225SvJFmRUTQB3hyHNa.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807182202250AiPnVj3JblqEfUF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220225HUdIj5D9Ayz2uYB8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.fermliving.com/webshop/shop/kids-room/kids-lamps/cloud-lamp-mint.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">ferm LIVING</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Blom Lamp by Andreas Engesvik</h3><p>Blom 台灯由挪威设计师 Andreas Engesvik 设计，制造商是意大利灯具品牌 Fontana Arte。造型巧妙，线条利落。灯体高 24 厘米，宽 15 厘米，使用者可以随意拿到需要它的地方。</p><p>Blom 这个名字取自挪威的一种花，灯光强弱可以调节。它适于放置在咖啡桌、床头柜上，给使用者带来愉悦的光影体验。售价 291 美元，<a href=\"https://hivemodern.com/pages/product7503/blom-table-lamp-andreas-engesvik-fontana-arte\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018071822031037fmjOzVEFck59WG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807182203100jRwyG4n6KSJhbCN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220310IZ53qukgA7hCQKbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.028571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220310i3pPoXCcyYZDjkuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220311OU5vE7r2z0LgdFeB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://hivemodern.com/pages/product7503/blom-table-lamp-andreas-engesvik-fontana-arte\" rel=\"nofollow\">hive</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Dish of Desire Bird Feeders by Frederik Roijé</h3><p>荷兰设计师 Frederik Roijé，一直是一个很有童趣，且对大自然怀有充分热情的人。最近，他设计了一款名为 Dish of Desire 的喂食装置，可以通过不同的变体，成为四种不同的喂食器。</p><p>Dish of Desire 由细骨瓷、铝材和红雪松木部件组成，构成一个简单的悬挂式喂食器。同时也把鸟类进食的过程变成了可以欣赏的舞台，观赏性和装饰性兼具。售价 79 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.roije.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=88\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220353fO49arNVA3whqXuG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807182203535RbUmQhvsEIqGXNf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220353XeDcHSrwytE8pnC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220354k53RgBf4lOnhYLwd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.roije.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=88\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frederik Roijé</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Levoop by Dreamfarm</h3><p>澳洲创意餐厨用品品牌 Dreamfarm 推出新品 Levoop，这是是一款可精准调节容量的量勺，还拿下了今年红点奖的产品设计奖。</p><p>它的特点在于可调整捞取容量，刮刀环是关键。适用于咖啡粉、奶粉、乳清蛋白和洗衣粉等，测量容量在 5 至 46.7 毫升以及 7 至 14 克之间。不含 BPA 的树脂材质，确保食用安全性。售价 9.95 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Dreamfarm-Levoop-Adjustable-Measuring-Multicolor/dp/B0784WZLFZ?tag=yankodesign05-20\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220623ronylIRVe8FwHf1Y.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220542BHUaochxPgv7wVql.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220542PkcmfibdLBXNhT91.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220542nHEhA1x6tW4P5TCV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180718220542TFBG2LCvHrQ0pefo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/07/17/the-levoop-is-a-super-duper-coffee-scooper/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}